    <mxCell id="assess" value="&lt;b&gt;Feasibility Assessment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;LLM analysis (adversarial)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Can we build this?&lt;br&gt;2. Does it deliver the RFE?&lt;br&gt;3. Is the effort estimate credible?&lt;br&gt;4. Hidden dependencies?&lt;br&gt;5. What's harder than it looks?" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e8e8e8;strokeColor=#333333;strokeWidth=2;arcSize=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=5;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" vertex="1" parent="1">
